usually in YAML, because it allows for comments, and is a bit shorter, but can be done in JSON.
Both can be mixed, but usually you don't, except for stuff like arrays: 
```yaml
  arrayOfNumbers: [ 1, 2, 3 ] # Abbreviated array representation
```
should expand on the info object:
https://spec.openapis.org/oas/v3.1.0#info-object

